import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome'
import { solid} from '@fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core/import.macro'

const StudentsLinks =  [
    { id: "1", link: '/', name:'Dashboard', icon: <FontAwesomeIcon icon={solid('home')} /> },
    { id: "2", link: '/student/profile', name:'Profile', icon: <FontAwesomeIcon icon={solid('user-graduate')} /> },
    { id: "3", link: '/student/apply', name:'Apply', icon: <FontAwesomeIcon icon={solid('paper-plane')} /> },
    { id: "4", link: '/student/applications', name:'Applications', icon: <FontAwesomeIcon icon={solid('folder-tree')} /> },
    { id: "5", link: '/student/courses', name:'Courses', icon: <FontAwesomeIcon icon={solid('layer-group')} /> },
    { id: "6", link: '/student/exams', name:'Exams', icon: <FontAwesomeIcon icon={solid('folder-open')} /> },
  ]











module.exports = { StudentsLinks };
